{
  "stem": "8775.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know exactly how they did it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, but there was food available.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the main thing was that the ghetto was just a, a transition point from worse things to come.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So even if it was food available and were somewhat sanitary facilities available, that was just a transitory period, what we had in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but the entrances were strictly controlled.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, they put up wooded gates.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything was, was gated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a wooded gate around it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was-- constantly, it was patrolled by the, by the gendarmes and the local police, too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But mainly the gendarmes we had to, we had to watch.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, the SS was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, so you didn't try to, to escape from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no escaping from there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were trying to maintain order.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some people became real depressed and suicidal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some people tried to take advantage, perhaps, of another person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They tried to-- well, the word is probably finagle a little more space or more food or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, it was the Jewish committee's responsibility to crack down on those abuses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mainly, they were just an instrument of the SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's, that's all they were, an instrument of the SS to carry out whatever the SS said that they wanted the people to do.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If they wanted the people to stand in line and get counted three times a day, the Jewish committee was responsible for that, to make sure that everybody knows that at certain time, at this time, there will be a, a listing or the numbering of the names.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you have to stand in line, you know, strict, erect, and don't do anything else at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was exactly 14.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
